original: Lundgren, Carl-Henrik, tandläkare, Borås, f. 11/6/09 i Sandhult, Älvsb. 1., av grosshandl. Carl L. o. Thyra Johanson. G. 34 m. Gullan Ann-Sofie Öquist. Barn i Göran f. 37, Gunilla o. Bertil 39, Birgitta 43. — Studiex. i Borås 27, tandl ikand. 29, tandl. 32. Prakt, i Borås sed. 32. Skattmäst. i Borås tandl isällsk. 34-40, ordf. där 42-45, ordf. i Västergötl. tandl ifören. 44.
translated: Lundgren, Carl-Henrik, dentist, Borås, b. 11/6/09 in Sandhult, Älvsborg County, son of the wholesale merchant Carl L. and Thyra Johanson. Married in 1934 to Gullan Ann-Sofie Öquist. Children: Göran, b. 1937; Gunilla and Bertil, b. 1939; Birgitta, b. 1943. - Graduated from Borås High School in 1927, dental studies in 1929, and became a dentist in 1932. Practiced in Borås since 1932. Treasurer of Borås Dental Society from 1934 to 1940, chairman from 1942 to 1945, chairman of the Västergötland Dental Association in 1944.
